1. Introduction
1.1 Motivation

Modern deep learning excels at single tasks but struggles with:

    Multi-task learning: Interference between tasks

    Continual learning: Catastrophic forgetting

    Task interpolation: Smooth transition between behaviors

    Uncertainty estimation: Knowing when the model is uncertain

1.2 Our Approach: Temporal Manifolds

We propose representing a family of models as a continuous trajectory through weight space:
